Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.70,0:01:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第十四話\N拯救小生命 美女醫生惠的挑戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.98,0:01:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恩！真是個美好的早晨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.12,0:01:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼清新的早晨\N就要用清水洗淨身體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.46,0:02:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又能讓精神舒暢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.09,0:02:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.00,0:02:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,閃到腰…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.71,0:02:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以薰姑娘和禰彥\N就到醫院幫忙去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.61,0:02:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心 我覺得你去較妥當
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.18,0:02:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼說？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.42,0:02:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對呀！那兩人能做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.59,0:02:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是惠姑娘真的很缺人手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.86,0:02:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唉！反正跟我沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.30,0:02:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要哭喔！吞下這個就會好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.34,0:02:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還沒輪到我嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.84,0:02:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去看看！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.27,0:02:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣固定住就沒問題了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.97,0:02:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,暫時不要動到傷口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.31,0:02:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.24,0:02:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰姑娘！你那邊還好吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.05,0:03:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀！真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.25,0:03:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不乖乖的就好不了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.05,0:03:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在幹嘛啊？阿薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.15,0:03:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.39,0:03:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請叫下一位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.02,0:03:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老婆婆！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.26,0:03:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.10,0:03:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇哈哈！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.40,0:03:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別跑！好痛！你們兩個!\N拜託到外面去玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.17,0:03:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.30,0:03:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會給你藥\N每天早晚要按時吃一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.94,0:03:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.18,0:03:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…女大夫…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.41,0:03:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恩！別擔心錢的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.95,0:03:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只想幫你治好病
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.35,0:03:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！老是這麼麻煩你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.26,0:03:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,醫生！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.33,0:03:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,醫生！嗚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.03,0:03:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.30,0:03:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他在賭場被菱萬字\N那夥人用木炮打傷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.23,0:03:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那夥人拿著木炮到處亂射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.70,0:03:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待會再說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.84,0:03:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先處理 不然會有生命危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.07,0:03:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先讓他躺下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.71,0:04:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰姑娘幫我準備乾淨的布
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.94,0:04:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.08,0:04:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥你幫我準備消毒水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.01,0:04:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.55,0:04:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.15,0:04:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,振作點！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.12,0:04:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我先消毒傷口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.32,0:04:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要消毒嘍！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.66,0:04:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題吧？那女醫生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.60,0:04:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身體內有裂傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.36,0:04:24.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是刀傷有點麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.47,0:04:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幫我壓住他的手腳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.71,0:04:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.63,0:05:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.27,0:05:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呼！已經脫離險境了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.03,0:05:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.31,0:05:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎光臨！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.04,0:05:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有一位嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.54,0:05:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有！那女醫生真了得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.41,0:05:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,面不改色地縫傷口\N就像在縫衣服一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.89,0:05:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且那醫生還是個美女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.39,0:05:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！我也想生病\N讓她溫柔地幫我治療
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.89,0:05:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你先付清我的帳再生病吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.66,0:06:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘿嘿嘿！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.86,0:06:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再給我一碗飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.03,0:06:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？這班人是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.68,0:06:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呼…醫生 藥苦不苦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.12,0:06:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一點 不過忍耐一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.06,0:06:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喝了它你就會舒服多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.53,0:06:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小楓的情況到底怎麼樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.66,0:06:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不太樂觀 她的身體很虛弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.80,0:06:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這房間光線很不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.67,0:06:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要把她移到通光更好的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.70,0:06:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,醫生！請你用最貴的藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.67,0:06:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多少錢都沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.88,0:06:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你用最貴最好的\N請你一定要救救小楓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.28,0:06:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我開的藥跟玄齊醫生一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.82,0:06:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們一定要按時給她吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.42,0:07:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道他們還不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.56,0:07:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以為有錢什麼都可以嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.93,0:07:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有錢就可買回性命嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.36,0:07:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那女孩沒救了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.40,0:07:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果按時吃今天給的藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.34,0:07:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該很快就能康復
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.51,0:07:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是如果讓心臟負擔過重\N就隨時會有危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.28,0:07:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.82,0:07:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.82,0:07:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,肚子…突然好痛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.22,0:07:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,痛死我啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.86,0:07:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有沒有人趕快去叫醫生！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.13,0:07:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喔！等一下！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.03,0:07:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別擔心 鎮上最好的醫生人在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.27,0:07:50.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,診所的女醫生嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.51,0:07:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是她沒錯！ 她前陣子用針縫傷口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.87,0:07:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是醫生嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.81,0:07:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請救救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.25,0:07:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.11,0:08:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.42,0:08:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請等一下！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.88,0:08:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,痛死我啦！ 惠！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.35,0:08:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂！你難道見死不救嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.26,0:08:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是現在最有名的醫生嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.73,0:08:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難不成是你治不了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.93,0:08:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幫他看看嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.84,0:08:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼樣 女醫生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.44,0:08:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要看的只有病人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.38,0:08:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請讓開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.92,0:08:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,病人嗎？病人的話就交給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.49,0:08:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是雷光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.26,0:08:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在深山裏長期做著艱苦的修行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.00,0:08:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,病人給我治療一定會好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.21,0:08:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.87,0:09:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請救救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.21,0:09:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遠離穢土…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.18,0:09:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿比喇根沙加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.79,0:09:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈啊！呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.53,0:09:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遠離穢土…阿比喇根沙加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.94,0:09:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遠離穢土…阿比喇根沙加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.89,0:09:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.36,0:09:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把這喝下去就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.93,0:09:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是靠僊人神力得來的神水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.67,0:10:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦！好了！真的不痛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.41,0:10:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.04,0:10:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這人好厲害呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.48,0:10:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連手都不用碰就治好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.28,0:10:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雷光道長才是能治百病的僊師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.58,0:10:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雷光道長\N我家有人生病 請你幫我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.59,0:10:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麻煩你看看我先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.52,0:10:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥 你看到了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.33,0:10:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.76,0:10:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心 你覺得是真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.36,0:10:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的能靠神力治好病嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.17,0:10:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.17,0:10:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 那人真的痛得很厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.84,0:10:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是惠姑娘卻無動於衷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.64,0:10:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管他就走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.61,0:10:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說不定惠姑娘\N看到了大家看不到的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.15,0:10:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼地方？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.22,0:10:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個我也不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.39,0:10:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恩！真的嗎？ 哎呀呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.46,0:11:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進行得很順利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.23,0:11:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣下去那個厲害的女醫生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.13,0:11:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就會被人家當成蒙古大夫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.77,0:11:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後她的病人\N就會慢慢轉向我們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.47,0:11:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說是嗎？雷光道長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.91,0:11:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是當然啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.81,0:11:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我雷光和你們菱萬字聯手\N哪有不成功的道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.92,0:11:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不論出多高價
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.52,0:11:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們還是會乖乖拿出錢的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.82,0:11:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.82,0:11:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不久我們就會成為富翁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.72,0:11:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿酒來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.36,0:11:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們先為這筆橫財慶祝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.16,0:11:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘿嘿！先從那女醫師下手\N再把附近的醫生都擊垮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.54,0:11:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然在這裏治好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.71,0:11:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吳服店的老太太\N也是靠雷光道長祈福治好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.25,0:11:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神明的力量真…啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.02,0:11:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恩哼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.49,0:12:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不是診所的女醫生嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.59,0:12:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她可是現在的話題人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.53,0:12:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒙古大夫！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.63,0:12:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼！再說一次！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.27,0:12:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個女的是蒙古大夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.80,0:12:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們說話小心點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.60,0:12:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.24,0:12:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,見死不救的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.61,0:12:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼會這樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.65,0:12:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說很厲害呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.22,0:12:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雷光道長在治好的病人間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.32,0:12:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,風評好得不得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.22,0:12:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過他只醫有錢人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.86,0:12:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雷光祈禱求來的神水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.53,0:12:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,據說要花很多錢才買得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.13,0:12:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有散播女醫生壞話的\N就是菱萬字那幫人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.63,0:12:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,菱萬字？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.20,0:12:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是在賭場\N用木炮射人的那班傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.01,0:12:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,簡直無法無天 比流氓還惡劣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.41,0:12:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.61,0:13:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來女醫生\N被麻煩的傢伙給盯上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.53,0:13:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.57,0:13:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,病人送來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.60,0:13:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.01,0:13:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們要對小楓做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.37,0:13:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.07,0:13:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以隨便移動她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.34,0:13:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然蒙古女大夫醫不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.65,0:13:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有請雷光道長出馬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.35,0:13:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以！不可以呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.69,0:13:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,滾開！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.69,0:13:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你幹什麼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.96,0:13:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,煩死了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.36,0:13:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們太過份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.10,0:13:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,見死不救\N沒用的蒙古大夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.51,0:14:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點閃開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.81,0:14:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可原諒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.85,0:14:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.95,0:14:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放開她！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.68,0:14:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,光靠祈禱是治不好病的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.46,0:14:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我決不能讓他們拿人命開玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.40,0:14:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,包在我身上\N我跟蹤到他們的去處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.23,0:14:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打他們個措手不及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.10,0:14:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！可惡的病魔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.31,0:14:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遠離穢土…阿比喇根沙加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.82,0:14:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遠離穢土…阿比喇根沙加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.54,0:15:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬上給我住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.01,0:15:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.12,0:15:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我正在祈禱的最高峰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.02,0:15:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,金倉先生你還不懂嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.65,0:15:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要治好小楓不能靠錢的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.12,0:15:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,親…親愛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.59,0:15:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人家不是說\N你棄痛苦的病人不救？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.60,0:15:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是裝的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.37,0:15:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒生病的人哪有救他的道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.77,0:15:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.77,0:15:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡！你說什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.97,0:15:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們是來找麻煩的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.74,0:15:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙不就是當時的病人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.95,0:15:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是又怎麼樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.08,0:15:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我決不會留你們活口的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.42,0:15:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這到底…該不會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.02,0:15:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在才覺悟不嫌太晚嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.09,0:15:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們都被這些人給騙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.50,0:16:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.90,0:16:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們都給我出來 菱萬字…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.17,0:16:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想打架我奉陪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.51,0:16:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.74,0:16:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是什麼人？給我殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.39,0:16:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們的動作實在太慢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.17,0:16:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.13,0:16:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惠！那女孩！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.91,0:16:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小楓！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.08,0:16:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會讓你壞我好事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.33,0:17:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,醫生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.03,0:17:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在你沒事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.03,0:17:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真…真是太感謝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.77,0:17:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我該怎麼謝你才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.67,0:17:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用謝！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.37,0:17:23.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只要你們記住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.58,0:17:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,治病不僅要正確的治療方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.92,0:17:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還要周圍親人的溫情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.82,0:17:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是花錢就能治好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.02,0:17:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,危險！大家都趴下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.96,0:17:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敢向菱萬字挑戰 真有膽量！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.74,0:17:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你那木炮管用嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.61,0:17:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這時候還開玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.31,0:18:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.65,0:18:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手！我的房子被炸壞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.69,0:18:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂！給我出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.36,0:18:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不然我把你們全炸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.10,0:18:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你就炸看看吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.73,0:18:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我人不舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.50,0:18:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說有蒙古道長有妙藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.71,0:18:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我特地過來看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.71,0:18:27.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.48,0:18:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們不覺得做得過火嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.45,0:18:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.75,0:18:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一個流浪劍客拽什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.55,0:18:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我手上可有這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.05,0:18:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給我射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.69,0:18:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.53,0:18:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我這逆刃刀\N除了人以外什麼都能砍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.20,0:18:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,廢話少說 給我上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.22,0:19:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然不是劍心的對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.76,0:19:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇啊！救命啊！\N我的腸子破了！痛死我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.24,0:19:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你就自己祈禱神水救你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.57,0:19:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的祈禱是假的 怎能治病呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.58,0:19:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於自己承認了吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.38,0:19:38.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.58,0:19:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.51,0:19:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果放著不管\N腸子爛了只有死路一條
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.09,0:19:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是答應我的條件 我才救你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.66,0:19:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.29,0:19:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不是雷光道長家嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.03,0:19:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唉呀！這麼吵鬧真不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.70,0:19:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂！大家快看！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.47,0:20:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雷光向眾人承認自己是假的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.07,0:20:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待會到我診所來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.64,0:20:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別管他們 這樣他們才不會為非作歹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.91,0:20:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,醫生要行仁術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.14,0:20:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,醫人不分善惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.88,0:20:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也要看一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.58,0:20:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像這種小傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.28,0:20:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒必要一一治療
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.03,0:20:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.16,0:20:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雷光那傢伙一下子就止痛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.96,0:20:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個藥叫什麼來著？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.07,0:20:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呼哈哈…咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.87,0:20:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個只是平常的水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.01,0:20:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.94,0:20:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,光喝水就能治好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.14,0:20:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！那個白癡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.45,0:20:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,玄齊醫生你的腰\N能治好真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.22,0:20:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最近我出去看診\N大家都問怎麼不是女醫生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.26,0:21:00.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說的也是 哈哈哈！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.50,0:21:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 真羨慕惠姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.33,0:21:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最近都沒人來學劍術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.67,0:21:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然同樣是師父
